ing and other primarily represent", "bbox": [151.3, 798.7, 1147.2, 821.3]}, {"text": "changes in the Company's estimates of when proved reserve quantities will be realized. During the twelve months ended", "bbox": [151.3, 823.2, 1147.2, 845.8]}, {"text": "December 31, 2013, the Company's undiscounted future net cash flows from proved reserves declined; however, the timing", "bbox": [151.3, 847.7, 1147.0, 870.3]}, {"text": "of the recovery of the future net cash flows accelerated, partially due to the removal of lower-return-on-investment vertical", "bbox": [151.3, 872.2, 1147.2, 894.8]}, {"text": "well locations, resulting in an increase in Standardized Measure.", "bbox": [151.3, 896.7, 677.6, 919.4]}]}